Tesla’s wild ride
Shares of Tesla TSLA, -2.72% rose 56% during January. Then the stock popped another 20% on Feb. 3, climbed 14% on Feb. 4 and dropped 17% on Feb. 5, before a rather mellow Feb. 6, when it rose 2%. Tomi Kilgore explains the technical trading patterns.

